OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783700376
OL,3,CFour kayakers rescued after being
OL,4,Cswept off Mull of Galloway
OL,6,FFour kayakers were wept off the Mull
OL,7,Fof Galloway in dense fog on Wednesday
OL,8,Fmorning, with one person reported
OL,9,Fmissing.
OL,11,FPortpatrick RNLI's all weather life-
OL,12,Fboat was called out at 7:39am , and
OL,13,Fwhilst en route the crew received an
OL,14,Fupdate confirming that three of the
OL,15,Fkayakers had managed to reach the
OL,16,Frocks at the Mull of Galloway, while
OL,17,Fone casualty remained missing at sea.
OL,19,FAfter checking those already traced
OL,20,Fwere in no immediate danger, the
OL,21,Fsearch for the fourth continued.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
