CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783700376
OL,3,CFour kayakers rescued after being
OL,4,Cswept off Mull of Galloway
OL,6,FAround an hour later, the 'exhausted'
OL,7,Fcasualty was found around 2.5 miles
OL,8,Foff the Mull of Galloway.
OL,10,FPortpatrick RNLI said, "Using the
OL,11,Fprevailing conditions, together with
OL,12,Fthe navigator's local knowledge of the
OL,13,Farea and tidal streams, the crew
OL,14,Fcalculated the likely drift of the
OL,15,Fmissing kayaker and identified a
OL,16,Fsearch area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783700376
OL,3,CFour kayakers rescued after being
OL,4,Cswept off Mull of Galloway
OL,6,F"At 8.31am, the casualty was spotted
OL,7,Fapproximately 2.5 miles off the Mull
OL,8,Fof Galloway. Although exhausted, the
OL,9,Fkayaker was recovered safely aboard
OL,10,Fthe lifeboat."
OL,12,FThe casualty was transferred to the
OL,13,Findependent Port William Inshore
OL,14,FRescue Service (PIRSAC) inshore
OL,15,Flifeboat crew, who had rescued the
OL,16,Fother three kayakers from the rocks.
OL,18,FAll four casualties were then safely
OL,19,Freturned to East Tarbet Bay.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
