OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783700376
OL,3,CFour kayakers rescued after being
OL,4,Cswept off Mull of Galloway
OL,6,FCoxswain Simon Bage said, "The dense
OL,7,Ffog made this a particularly
OL,8,Fchallenging search, but thanks to our
OL,9,Fnavigator's local knowledge of the
OL,10,FMull of Galloway and understanding of
OL,11,Fthe tidal streams, we were able to
OL,12,Fidentify the most likely search area
OL,13,Fand locate the missing kayaker quickly.
OL,15,F"This was an excellent example of the
OL,16,Fteamwork between Belfast Coastguard,
OL,17,FPIRSAC and Portpatrick RNLI, and I'm
OL,18,Fincredibly proud of the
OL,19,Fprofessionalism and dedication shown
OL,20,Fby our volunteer crew.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
