PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783700376
OL,3,CFour kayakers rescued after being
OL,4,Cswept off Mull of Galloway
OL,6,F"Their training, commitment and
OL,7,Fwillingness to respond at any time of
OL,8,Fday or night are what enable us to
OL,9,Fsave lives at sea."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
